description: Step inside this thoughtfully laid out 2 bed/1.5 bath duplex condo to discover a sun-drenched open concept living space featuring a fireplace, high ceilings, hardwood floors, the convenience of a half bathroom and direct access to a PRIVATE balcony and oversized patio offering space for ample seating and dining and your very own vegetable garden! The kitchen boasts granite countertops, white cabinetry, stainless-steel appliances, bar seating for 2 and a separate dining area. The two bedrooms in the lower level share a full bathroom with one bedroom able to accommodate a bed and desk. Additional unit features include central A/C, in-unit laundry, all new paint throughout and updated light fixtures. Located in the heart of South Boston's sought-after East Side, you’re just minutes from Castle Island, M Street Beach, trendy local restaurants, cafes with easy access to public transportation. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or investor, don’t miss out on this great opportunity!
